      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. The vehicle features an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original factory character. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical perfection, this unit represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver who values automotive excellence and meticulous preservation.",
