      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this car. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and I've taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s basically in showroom condition! It\u2019s been kept in a garage, pampered with regular detailing, and drives like a total dream. You really won't find one cleaner than this; it looks and smells brand new. I'm looking for a quick, smooth sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions. I'd love for this beauty to go to a great new home!",
