    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated ZF 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, with a documented VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement already completed for long-term structural integrity. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings and original dampers, ensuring the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the variable M differential lock operates silently. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-tier specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. One owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Full service history. Inspection welcome.",
