    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a truly mint-condition vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, glass-like factory luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and climate-controlled garage storage. Every body panel is perfectly aligned with original factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under the original floor mats, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously maintained with a full-service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships, using only OEM parts. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of leaks or corrosion, and the transmission shifts with surgical precision. This sale includes all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a thick folder of maintenance receipts. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
