    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it\u2019s still in absolutely flawless condition! If you\u2019re looking for that perfect 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. It's been such a joy to own, and I know you're going to love it just as much as I have. Come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
