    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a masterclass in preservation. At its heart lies the 2JZ-GTE inline-six, retaining its factory sequential twin-turbocharging system and exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders. Power is delivered through the robust Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, with the double-wishbone suspension and all OEM bushings maintaining factory-spec geometry. Every vacuum line, seal, and electrical connector remains supple, showing no signs of the heat-cycling fatigue common in high-performance Japanese classics. This is a collector-grade example for the purist who values mechanical integrity and unmolested engineering above all else.",
